[h3 
	" About the game
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Metal Max is a classic RPG that released by DATA EAST in Japen in the year 1991. It's famous for it's two modes of battle including human-battle and tank-battle. The high degree of freedom is also a significant feature in this game. The background of the story is set in future that a major disaster occurs on Earth and many monsters rampage everywhere. The hero pursues his dream of becoming a hunter and be kicked out the house by his father.In this game there are eight tanks available for collection and eleven wanted available challenge. The final condition to complete the game is to defeat the boss Noah and go home then you will see the Chinese characters "å®Œ" means "The End" after a long trailers video.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"This movie mainly used three major glitches. The hero and partner gets on the same tank at the same time will copy a tank. When use a pharmacy to trailer the ATK of the hero will be close to the maximum. After fire a panic bomb to enemy by tank there will be a chance to make it to escape.
	$LF
]p
